==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nonmoral
<hw>Non*mor"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Neither moral nor
immoral; having no connection with morals; not within the sphere of
morals or ethics; not ethical; <as>as, imagination is of its nature
<ex>nonmoral</ex>; infants are <ex>nonmoral</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nonmoving</ent>⟦br⟧
